%F A008451 G.f.: theta_3(0,x)^7, where theta_3 is the third Jacobi theta function. - _Robert Israel_, Jul 16 2014
%F A008451 a(n) = (14/n)*Sum_{k=1..n} A186690(k)*a(n-k), a(0) = 1. - _Seiichi Manyama_, May 27 2017
